name: Denzil Ritchie
text: Donatos is one of my favorite pizza places to order from.  This location seems to have a bunch of employees who care about there jobs and like what they are doing.  Super friendly crew!  The pizzas from here are always hot, fresh and consistently good.  If you're in this area, I would highly suggest you order from this location.

name: Jamisen Hilvers
text: I wish every restaurant experience was like this...From order through pick-up, the staff was knowledgeable, friendly and helpful... Our order was made exactly as we had requested, was hot, and was ready super quick for us to pick up!! Thanks Donatos Five Oaks Staff!!
